      "raw_text": "A large and enthusiastic meeting\nor the Telephone Operators union\nwas held this noon in the new rooms\nOF the organization at Sprague and\nMill street to consider several mat\ntiers concerning the strike inaugural\ned by the girls last week. The FIRST\nbusiness was that pertaining to the\nschedule OF assignments for picket\nduty during the present week, The\nentire tone of the meeting was one\nof united effort. with no slipping,\nagainst the Pacific Telephone & Tele-\ngraph company.\n\n\nThe chief matter of Importance to\nthe general public was that of de-\nclaring q boycott Of the company"
